es/año en atención primaria","guid":"ZuEi6R6nIVIkHjMmW6sV2g","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"75% localizada (50% cabeza/cuello), 25% generalizada (enfermedad sistémica)","guid":"Y4n4S0nv7dAIvCHzLkLq_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Edad >40 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"Sexo masculino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"Raza blanca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"Ubicación supraclavicular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"16","text":"Síntomas sistémicos (fiebre, sudoración nocturna, pérdida de peso)","guid":"Gw0Yu3SY-qQ6inHXKJhywQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Anamnesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Duración y evolución de linfadenopatía","guid":"W25_ZhE2WBAELY17WZws-A","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"Historial médico de infecciones, malignidad, enf. autoinmunes","guid":"L9NJpzEaPNxy_j1AWl7NKQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"Exposiciones recientes, viajes, contacto animales","guid":"XIt1QgNj4_1kREYpLMaCsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"Examen físico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Revisión completa de sistemas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Examen linfático focalizado: tamaño, consistencia, movilidad","guid":"W_YKvxvdxTxjgjEOQ6x1SA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"HEENT, torácico, abdominal, pélvico según síntomas asociados","guid":"QoEXbxZRF-59n1kLKWI6WA","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"22","text":"Señales de alarma\\Npara malignidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Diámetro >1cm (2cm en inguinales)","guid":"NPg5QSG9jDIFDVAzGIIxjA","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Consistencia dura","guid":