opatológico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Criterios dependen de etiología específica","guid":"G5Qcxnv_mB1fNqxqHfaJkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos diferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Neoplásico: linfomas, leucemias, metástasis, neoplasias de piel","guid":"fU8mfA6Jseh7x3XAD9UM7A","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Infeccioso: viral, bacteriano, micobacteriano, fúngico, parasitario","guid":"QgpE4jM0juhSLj0EJqUUuQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"Autoinmune: LES, AR, enfermedad mixta tejido conectivo, Sjögren, enfermedad relacionada a IgG4","guid":"XZ_lUG7mOkRny1nSC28ftg","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"Misceláneos: sarcoidosis, histiocitosis, enfermedad de Castleman, enfermedad de Kawasaki","guid":"b-J9rlW4IZ0VNGTaDLyGUw","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"52","text":"Iatrogénico: medicamentos, enfermedad del suero","guid":"Jycad2KmH0dsF6ZoDucrPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Basado en causa subyacente","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Malignidad: quimioterapia, radioterapia, cirugía","guid":"LbcywHTVANUrn3VIGoXSag","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Infección: antibióticos, antivirales, antifúngicos según etiología","guid":"Ap-rdWDZ8N1zAewXHjPIOw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"Autoinmune: corticosteroides, inmunosupresores","guid":"XNmI-lI4mIE8KlHLWiivdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"Evitar terapia empírica sin diagnóstico definitivo","guid":"YMJKaTfxx4tp_bxjIsyPTA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y pronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Depende de etiología específica","guid":"ayZWczwr-WdJcaQFSMY7ww","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Malignidad: estadificación, respuesta a tratamiento","guid":"K